# Defence in depth: NEVER commit plaintext secrets (PRD §18, CLAUDE.md §12).
# Only *.example.yaml templates and sealed (ciphertext-only) objects are tracked.
*.plain.yaml
*.plaintext.yaml
*.dec.yaml
*.env
.env
.env.*
# Allow the examples and the sealed (encrypted) outputs.
!*.example.yaml
!sealed/*.sealed.yaml
